&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;3+ years of charge entry and billing experience, preferably in behavioral health&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strict attention to details&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of payer specific billing requirements&lt;/li&gt;
