&lt;li&gt;Conduct regular team meetings and 1:1s to provide ongoing feedback and support.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the continuous improvement of programs by reviewing care coach performance, client outcomes, and feedback to identify areas for growth.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the onboarding and ongoing training of new care coaches.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
